high_descs: Turn right, head towards the toilet, and then turn right towards the sink.
Pick up the bar soap inside the sink.
Turn left towards the bath tub.
Place the bar soap in between the middle and right towel in the tub.
Turn around and head towards the white dresser beside the sink.
Pick up the bar soap on top of the dresser.
Turn left and head towards the tub.
Place the bar soap next to the right of the other soap in the tub.
anns.task_desc: Place the two bar soaps inside the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around and walk to the sink behind you and to the right
pick up the soap out of the sink
Turn to the left and walk to the tub
Place the soap in the tub between the right and middle cloth.
Turn to the right and walk to the white cabinet on the left.
Open the white cabinet and take out the soap in it.
Turn to the left and walk to the tub across the room.
Place the soap in the tub under the cloth on the right.
anns.task_desc: Place two bars of soap into the bath tub.

high_descs: Turn around and go left to face the sink.
Pick up the bar of soap from the sink.
Turn to the left to face the tub.
Put the soap in to the tub.
Turn to the right and face the cabinet next to the sink.
Pick up the soap that is on the cabinet.
Turn to the left and face the tub.
Place the soap in the tub next to the other soap.
anns.task_desc: Place two soaps in the tub next to each other.
